<emphasis box="[1020,1083,1209,1235]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="114">2–SR</emphasis>
1.4 times as long as width of pterostigma (Fig. 94). Scape and pedicel variably brownish yellow to brown. fm: 
<quantity box="[670,814,1276,1302]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" metricValueMax="2.1" metricValueMin="1.9" pageId="17" pageNumber="114" unit="mm" value="2.0" valueMax="2.1" valueMin="1.9">1.9–2.1 mm</quantity>
